MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

94-1890. No. 65359. Faber v. Syed. Cuyahoga County,

This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective March 2, 1995.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and is hereby, dismissed.
